HEADWORD: paternalistic
<hw>pa*ter`nal*ist"ic</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Benevolent but sometimes
intrusive; -- used often of governments and the administration of large
organizations. See <cref>paternal government</cref>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

